      "objective": "Map the emotional and informational journey the reader must travel through this post \u2014 based on the intent they arrived with. The post must deliver on the promise of the metadata from start to finish.",
      "principle": "The reader clicked because of a specific promise in the title and description. Every section of the post must honour that promise. If they came for inspiration \u2014 every H2 feeds that. If they came for a decision \u2014 every H2 moves them closer to it. No section breaks the journey.",
